    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/bc6ca221d4457548e3121d866cdddb28.avif?t=1737507265\" width=616 height=173 /></span><br><br>游戏作者Brigitta Rena，其他游戏作品包括：《乌鸦先生的独白》（A Raven Monologue）和《光之传承者》（She &amp; The Light Bearer）<br><br>《往室》（When the Past was Around）是一款点击互动式解谜冒险游戏，讲述了一段关于热恋，放手再到释怀的故事，以及其中苦乐参半的点点滴滴。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/fd8adeed13b77e4974112ef6316bfc1f.poster.avif?t=1737507265\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/fd8adeed13b77e4974112ef6316bfc1f.webm?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/fd8adeed13b77e4974112ef6316bfc1f.mp4?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>故事的主人公叫Eda，一个二十出头的女孩。<br>她和每一个同龄人一样不知所措。<br>她在实现梦想的路上迷失方向；<br>又在追寻真爱的途中误入歧途。<br><br>直到Owl来到了她身边——<br><br>是他，让她重燃了追梦的热情；<br>是他，满足了她对爱情的憧憬；<br>同样也是他，让她领悟了心碎的滋味。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/6cd03e91cb5597bf776d9259f0fe357a.poster.avif?t=1737507265\" width=616 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/6cd03e91cb5597bf776d9259f0fe357a.webm?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/6cd03e91cb5597bf776d9259f0fe357a.mp4?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这个虚幻的世界里，女孩和恋人曾流连过的房间交织在一起，其中所承载的欢喜与泪水，正是这对恋人支离破碎的过去。每搜集一条线索，解开一道谜题，打开一扇门，女孩都能离曾经的秘密更进一步——那些她曾深藏心中，专属于她和恋人之间的秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/661eddb9a8527b272d5a64d329d6ce6a.avif?t=1737507265\" width=616 height=159 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/f0b0ef855f86e98d5af753accc0ef0d3.poster.avif?t=1737507265\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/f0b0ef855f86e98d5af753accc0ef0d3.webm?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/f0b0ef855f86e98d5af753accc0ef0d3.mp4?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>独特而又能唤起情感共鸣的故事。这是一款关于战胜过去，重拾自我的游戏。<br></li><li>看看自己的百宝盒，喝点茶，或是洗洗衣服——解开在日常的琐事中的谜题，找寻那些过去的秘密。<br></li><li>在一系列极具生活气息的手绘场景中踏上一段美妙的异想之旅。<br></li><li>从安逸的日常，到揪心的别离，小提琴伴奏无时不在，为您带来沉浸式的体验。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/cbada9aa051d0ac3d2f8f17f0424b5ab.poster.avif?t=1737507265\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/cbada9aa051d0ac3d2f8f17f0424b5ab.webm?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/cbada9aa051d0ac3d2f8f17f0424b5ab.mp4?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《往室》是一款全程无对话的叙事类游戏，仅用不到两个小时即可通关。流程虽短，却也是我们的心血之作。我们竭力想要为您献上一段深入内心，回味无穷的旅程。希望您与Eda和Owl渡过的短暂时光，会成为珍贵而难忘的回忆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/6cd03e91cb5597bf776d9259f0fe357a.poster.avif?t=1737507265\" width=616 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/6cd03e91cb5597bf776d9259f0fe357a.webm?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1164050/extras/6cd03e91cb5597bf776d9259f0fe357a.mp4?t=1737507265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
